Module takMashido.shani
Package takMashido.shani.orders

Class KeywordOrder

java.lang.Object
takMashido.shani.orders.Order
takMashido.shani.orders.TextOrder
takMashido.shani.orders.KeywordOrder
public abstract class KeywordOrder
extends TextOrder
Represents order activated by a single keyword. Supports creating multiple targets with it's own keywords represented by KeywordAction class. Creation of KeywordAction registers it in inner targets List and mainFile Document object.

To execute Actions do not having specified keywords override UnmatchedAction class and return it's instance from getUnmatchedAction(ShaniString) or getUnmatchedAction() method.

Loading of targets stored in MainFile is done in actionFactory(Element).

Author:
TakMashido
